{
  "stem": "4226.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--towards the end of October.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was no snow on the ground yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to walk to this place and bring back the food container which was sent out to us, 50 liters for 50 people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when we arrived there, we dispersed, each to his own work in, in that place.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The three of us, the two engineers went in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The two Germans were living in two rooms in that electrical goods barrack.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The, the boss, or the head of the two Germans-- one was over the other-- was a very [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] rough man.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and he kept telling us to work faster.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But don't worry, because you'll never get liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You'll be killed before, before anyone gets liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we knew him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we knew the days when he wouldn't be there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went to Munich.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In, in the Munich Deutsches Museum was the headquarters of, of, of this organization.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He went to get his paperwork done there in the mornings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But normally, I had to put his bowl of water over his stove, make fire in his room.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and he dressed up, and washed himself, and cleared out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, I find that I could bake potatoes nicely in his stove.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] For his stove was going on timber or coal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you had the little handle which you moved, then the pot ash fall in the bottom chamber.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I filled it with potatoes and had nice baked potatoes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then, of course, we found that among the electrical goods, we had this spiral resistance, which you put in a bucket, and it will boil in about 20 minutes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's like a kettle has inside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, and portable, with a cable.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
